ComicInfo.Summary:
Dynamite proudly presents "Frank Cho's Jungle Girl"! Co-Plotted and overseen by Frank Cho, scripted by Doug Murray and crafted by artist Adriano Batista and Frank Martin, the Jungle Girl is destined to be THE Dynamite series of 2007! Issue #3 continues our debut Jungle Girl adventure as Jana's world continues to unfold around her unsuspecting companions! It's all heading towards the most dramatic and stunning conclusion ever seen in comics! Don't miss it! Featuring two covers, one by Mr. Jungle Girl himself, Frank Cho (shipping at 75%) and the variant chase cover by Batista (shipping at 25%)!
